          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-1" n="1">A Bard grown desirous of saving his Pelf</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-2" n="2">Built a House he was sure wou'd serve none but himself.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-3" n="3">This enrag'd God Apollo, who Mercury sent</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-4" n="4">And bid him go ask what his Votary meant.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-5" n="5">Some foe to my Empire has been his adviser,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-6" n="6">'Tis of dreadful portent when a Poet turns Miser.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-7" n="7">Tell him, Hermes, from me, tell that Subject of mine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-8" n="8">I have sworn by the Styx to defeat his design.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-9" n="9">For wherever he lives the Muses shall Reign,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C740L-line-10" n="10">And the Muses, he knows, have a numerous Train.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
